# Environment — never bake secrets or dev-only config into images
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Build outputs (regenerated inside the container)
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/dist
**/build
**/out

# VCS & editor
.git
.gitignore
.vscode
.idea
**/*.swp
**/*.swo

# Tests / CI
**/coverage
**/test-results
**/playwright-report
**/blob-report
**/.playwright

# OS
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Docs — not needed in runtime images
README.md
docs/
ARCHITECTURE.md
CLAUDE.md

# Foundry / Solidity workspace (not needed in the web image)
apps/contracts/cache
apps/contracts/out
apps/contracts/broadcast
